titles this year.
</P>
<P>
Davenport officially took over as the world's top player this
week. She will remain atop the world rankings another week.
Williams maintains her place at number five.
</P>
<P>
The win extends Davenport's five year winning streak in
Switzerland to 17 victories. She has not dropped a set for the
past two years at the Zurich tournament. 
