installments, it may be an oversight by my counterpart," Shamshad
said.
</P>
<P>
"The entire lot - every fisherman and every boat - that is in
Pakistan's custody is being released," he added.
</P>
<P>
Pakistani Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif, in a goodwill gesture,
Friday announced unilateral release of all Indian fishermen in
Pakistan's custody.
</P>
<P>
Pakistani Foreign Secretary Shamshad Saturday said Islamabad
has decided to release all Indian civilian prisoners.
</P>
<P>
Ragunath did not indicate the release of Pakistani civilian
detainees and said that the procedure with regard to these
prisoners was being speeded up. 
