<HEADLINE> CPC Senior Official Meets Cuban Delegation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 18 (Xinhua) -- Xie Fei, member of the
Political Bureau of the Chinese Communist Party Central Committee,
met today with a Cuban Communist Party (CCP) delegation led by
Rolando Vasquez, member of the CCP Central Committee and
