<P>
Vasquez said that China's experience in economic construction,
which Cuban leaders observed in their visits to China during the
past years, is now benefiting the ongoing economic restructuring
and enterprise reform in Cuba.
</P>
<P>
He also briefed his hosts on the political, economic and
diplomatic situation in his homeland. 
</P>
</TEXT>
