<HEADLINE> Sixth APPCED General Assembly Closes in Guilin (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Declaration urges "the tourism industry and tourists to
abide by those laws of the destination countries related to
natural resource conservation and environmental protection."
</P>
<P>
It also asks "the tourism administration and tourism business
operators to enhance the degree of cooperation and exchange so as
to strengthen the capacity of all countries to develop tourism in
a sustainable way".
</P>
