<HEADLINE> Romania Launches Poverty Alleviation Program </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, October 17 (Xinhua) -- Romanian President Emil
Constantinescu called Saturday for addressing the very roots of
poverty through the country's economic development.
</P>
